sub _check {
  my $self = shift;
  $self->SUPER::_check;
  my $bop = $self->{def}{string} || $self->{bop};
  $self->Error("You can only use '%s' between (non-negative) integers",$bop)
    unless $self->{lop}->class =~ /INTEGER|MINUS/ &&
           $self->{rop}->class eq 'INTEGER';
}
